803
00:40:52,572 --> 00:40:54,005
Dead two days later?

804
00:40:54,092 --> 00:40:55,571
LEO: He died from dum-dums?

805
00:40:55,652 --> 00:40:58,086
DOCTOR: We'll keep you overnight.
ROGER: Make it two.

806
00:40:58,172 --> 00:40:59,127
Two days?

807
00:40:59,212 --> 00:41:00,850
Okay, we'll keep him two days.

808
00:41:00,932 --> 00:41:02,081
Is that Leo's chart?

809
00:41:02,172 --> 00:41:04,561
DOCTOR: Two days,
then you'll be as good as new.

810
00:41:04,652 --> 00:41:06,210
LEO: I should be with them.

811
00:41:06,292 --> 00:41:08,044
I should be with... Ow, ow!

812
00:41:08,612 --> 00:41:10,204
How do you spell, "proctological"?

813
00:41:10,292 --> 00:41:11,805
ROGER: Rectal exam?

814
