Please, Mr. Getz.

817
00:41:17,452 --> 00:41:21,001
DOCTOR: You've been shot in the arm?
Let her take it. You'll get it back.

818
00:41:21,092 --> 00:41:23,322
DOCTOR: There's a clock in your room.

819
00:41:24,412 --> 00:41:26,084
