855
00:42:41,852 --> 00:42:43,490
Do you mind? Thanks.

856
00:42:45,532 --> 00:42:47,682
Sorry. I was just looking at it.

857
00:42:47,772 --> 00:42:49,410
Chew on this onion.

858
00:42:50,532 --> 00:42:52,409
He's quitting, so help him.

859
00:42:53,212 --> 00:42:54,850
I was only looking at it.

860
00:42:57,492 --> 00:42:59,323
ROGER: The first thing is the fat.

861
00:42:59,412 --> 00:43:01,607
ROGER: Everyone says, "Cut the fat."

862
00:43:01,972 --> 00:43:04,850
My uncle said, "You cut the fat,
you kill the burger." Right?

863
00:43:04,932 --> 00:43:05,967
EDDIE: Yeah.

864
00:43:06,052 --> 00:43:09,681
ROGER: There's an art to it.
You just can't plop this on the grill.

865
00:43:11,412 --> 00:43:13,642
ROGER: Gently coax the flavors out.

866
00:43:15,892 --> 00:43:17,723
Yo, hey, what's the problem?

867
00:43:24,252 --> 00:43:27,403
ROGER: A little pepper,
then you massage it a little bit.

868
00:43:27,812 --> 00:43:29,040
Just a little bit.

869
00:43:29,132 --> 00:43:31,202
[Sings] "Sweet, sweet meat"

870
00:43:34,052 --> 00:43:35,770
Shit, man, feel it.

871
00:43:39,332 --> 00:43:40,447
Okay, guys!

872
00:43:40,772 --> 00:43:42,524
RIGGS: LAPD. Let me see your hands.

873
00:43:42,612 --> 00:43:44,887
Let me see your hands! Get them up!

874
00:43:44,972 --> 00:43:48,521
RIGGS: In the car! Get them up there!
Let me see both of them! Come on!

875
00:43:48,612 --> 00:43:50,330
[Multiple gunshots]

876
00:43:52,332 --> 00:43:53,321
Hey, Riggs!

877
00:43:53,412 --> 00:43:54,606
[Gunshots]

878
00:43:55,852 --> 00:43:57,080
[Tires screech]

879
00:43:57,772 --> 00:43:59,251
[Riggs groans]

880
00:44:01,772 --> 00:44:02,648
Riggs!

881
00:44:04,012 --> 00:44:06,446
ROGER: Don't you love me? For five days!

882
00:44:07,492 --> 00:44:08,641
[Bang]

883
00:44:13,972 --> 00:44:15,405
Don't do that to me!

884
00:44:15,492 --> 00:44:17,369
ROGER: Riggs, are you okay?
RIGGS: Yeah.

885
00:44:17,452 --> 00:44:18,680
